Smart School Planner is the assistant for your school life and helps you organize your study. 

Whether it's grades, assignments, topics, circulars or absences, Smart School Planner is your partner to keep an eye on your progress and stay organized. 

Hi, my name is Giulio and when I was in high school I felt the need for an app like Smart School Planner. I studied programming languages ​​a bit and managed to develop it. At first, only my classmates used it, then also the rest of my school, and after a year, it became one of the most used apps by students in Italy. 

Today Smart School Planner has allowed me to found a startup to improve the lives of students and parents. 
I recently completely renewed the interface and started adding new features. 

Let me know what do you think, Smart School Planner was born from our needs. 

With Smart School Planner you can: 
• Check grades, assignments, arguments, circulars or absences; 
• Set an average to keep and know what grade you have to take; 
• Set reminders; 
• Record the lessons; 
• Mark important and already done tasks.

Terms of use: https://www.appregistro.it/en/tos.html

Con 4Milioni di quiz al suo interno, e con più di un 1Milione di utenti acquisiti nel corso di questi ultimi anni, il simulatore quiz di Concorsando.it. è oggettivamente il miglior simulatore per concorsi pubblici esistente sul mercato.

Disponibile sia nella versione di app mobile che sottoforma di portale web, con esso potrai esercitarti dovunque e in ogni momento, anche in offline, sulle banche dati ufficiali dei concorsi pubblici a cui stai partecipando.

Bada bene che in assenza di una banca dati ufficiale di solito la redazione di Concorsando.it, se si tratta di un concorso importante, crea una banca dati apposita per agevolare i candidati. In mancanza potrai comunque esercitarti separatamente sulle singole materie indicate nel bando. 

Rispetto ad ogni singola banca dati potrai: 
• studiare i quiz di cui si compone monitorando con estrema precisione, quiz per quiz, il tuo grado di apprendimento; 
• effettuare una o più prove personalizzate impostando autonomamente tutti i parametri (numero di domande per materia, tempo a disposizione e punteggi); 
• sfidare gli altri candidati in una vera e propria simulazione del concorso con tanto di graduatoria anonima: potrai effettuare un numero infinito di prove d’esame, la tua posizione in graduatoria sarà determinata dinamicamente in base al punteggio medio delle tue ultime 5 prove. 

Per ogni banca dati in particolare, dopo aver selezionato la materia o le materie che vuoi studiare, potrai restringere maggiormente il campo utilizzando una serie di filtri (ad esempio solo i quiz che contengono determinate parole chiave) e/o selezionando solo i quiz che rientrano in un determinato range di apprendimento (ad esempio solo i quiz che per te sono più ostici, ossia che sbagli sempre). 

Dopo aver impostato con precisione il tuo blocco di quiz potrai: 
• esercitarti su di esso; 
• stamparlo in ordine alfabetico; 
• rileggerlo nell’ordine originale, con la risposta esatta evidenziata; 
• riascoltarlo, nel senso che una voce sintetica per ogni quiz ti leggerà la domanda e la risposta esatta. 

Bello vero? 

Considera che ci sono ancora tante altre funzioni interessanti che agevoleranno il tuo studio. 

Prova subito il simulatore quiz di Concorsando.it, vedrai che lo troverai estremamente utile e funzionale!

Creative and educational game for children that will help your child spend time with an electronic device effectively. Let your child feel like a real artist. The app includes coloring activity which is friendly to the youngest as well as drawing lessons intended to develop fine motor skills. Also, the app contains pictures on different topics which will entertain your child with fascinating sounds and funny characters. The following is waiting for you:

- 9 topic packs with 135 pages;
- Easy coloring for children;
- Drawing lessons;
- Creativity development.

The app is designed for children of preschool age and also suitable for boys and girls 2- 4 years old. All the activities were developed with participation of experts in the field of children education and include such educational elements as developing of fine motor skills and logic. Have fun!

Creative coloring games for kids will help your child learn more about colors and coloring itself. Let your child become a real artist and develop new talents. Coloring book for kids includes coloring activity which is friendly to the youngest and focuses on different objects that are surrounding kids everyday. Furthermore, these games for kids contain a lot of coloring tools that will entertain your child with fascinating sounds and funny animations. The following is waiting for you:

- 9 topic packs with 144 coloring pages;
- Easy coloring book for kids;
- Different coloring tools for customizing;
- Creativity development.

Games for girls and boys are designed for children of preschool age and also suitable as games for toddlers of 2- 4 years old. All the activities were developed with participation of experts in the field of children education and include such educational games for girls and boys as fine motor skills and logic development. Enjoy!

Bimi Boo with you again! This time you will go to visit friends of Bimi Boo, who live in a treehouse. You will meet a sly cat, funny rabbit and cute squirrel. There is an exciting game in the house of your baby in which he can help to bring order, to place everything in its place and feed friends of Bimi Boo.

15 different games will fascinate a child with not only bright colors and funny animations, but also with interesting and clear tasks such as:

- Arrange items by color, shape, number and size;
- Pick up items within the meaning of;
- Arrange the geometric shapes according to silhouette;
- Sort items in its place
- Feed animals in a right way;
- Restore pictures from memory.

Together with Bimi Boo Shapes & Colors, your baby will learn to distinguish shapes, colors, texture and quantity. The game also improves fine motor skills, attention and intelligence. It contains everything you need for a fun and healthy development of the child.
